cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.SI

This paper deals with secure data exchange among partners, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also introduces a policy language for defining data exchange requirements, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper explores policy and performance trade-offs, which relates to social and information sciences (cs.SI).
